			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Help build the leading emotion analytics platform powered by the largest repository of emotional data in the world. Affectiva is looking for a highly talented and motivated Senior Data Scientist to join our team and build our emotion analytics capabilities. For a hard-core machine learning or statistics person who wants to take research out of the lab and into the real world, this is a dream job!</p>
<p>
	Responsibilities</p>
<p>
	Affectiva has the world&rsquo;s largest database of physiological and facial expressions of emotion, that tie to important key business metrics. The responsibilities of the Senior Data Scientist include:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Apply state-of-the-art statistical modeling/machine learning and data mining techniques to large amounts of noisy, complex real-world emotion data</li>
	<li>
		Advance our core emotion recognition algorithms to handle the reliable detection of rare emotion expressions</li>
	<li>
		Build models that tie emotion data to important key business metrics</li>
	<li>
		Extend our machine learning framework to handle rare events, as well as semi-supervised training and classification</li>
	<li>
		Work closely with Engineering to deliver algorithms into production systems</li>
</ul>
<p>
	Requirements</p>
<p>
	We&rsquo;re looking for passionate, motivated and entrepreneurial professionals to add to Affectiva&rsquo;s Science Team. Successful candidates for this role will have:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Advanced degree in Computer Science, Statistics, or related field</li>
	<li>
		Excellent programming skills (e.g., MATLAB, C/C++. Python, R)</li>
	<li>
		Experience in statistical or machine learning on medium-size or large-size data</li>
	<li>
		Experience with statistical modeling techniques, e.g., regression, decision trees, SVMs</li>
	<li>
		Experience using Map Reduce on frameworks such as Hadoop or Elastic Map Reduce</li>
</ul>
<p>
	Assets</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Expertise in facial / human behavior analysis, tracking and classification</li>
	<li>
		Commercial software development experience</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
